The '''Warehouse''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It increases the storage capacity for all resources. Enhanced by any bordering [[Sawmill]], [[Stonemason]], [[Mill]] or [[Foundry]].

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 1

